# Sage

## About

Sage will be a feature rich piece of software, in the future!

Currently; this project is not in a state where it can be considered 'in-development'. Hopefully that changes soon.
In the future, the scope will likely be an application framework and game engine, primarily for the purpose of developing video games.
The plan is to produce multiple demonstration applications/games, developed for the purpose of improving the engine over time and facilitating my own personal learning.

